article_id:2065,category_name:News,title_name:Announcing a Platinum Showcase! 5★ Gala Dragalia Adventurer Guaranteed!,image_path:,message:<div>A Platinum Showcase will start on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1616824800"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>The Platinum Showcase is a limited summon showcase that works similarly to a tenfold summon in that one summon will get you 10 results. The difference between a regular tenfold summon and this Platinum Showcase is that a 5★ Gala Dragalia adventurer available at the time of this summon showcase is guaranteed to appear.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Note: The roster for this summon showcase will not include the new adventurers from the Gala Dragalia showcase that will also be live at the same time.</span></div><div><br></div><div>During the period, players are limited to doing the Platinum Showcase summon five times, and these summons can only be performed with diamantium (purchase required).</div><div><br></div><div>Availability period for the Platinum Showcase:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1616824800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1618207199"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at some of the 5★ adventurers eligible to appear as the guaranteed 5★ summon below.</div><div><br></div><div>
